        "name": "Intalix - Food Delivery API",
        "description": "Complete API collection for the Intalix Food Delivery App.\nIncludes Auth, Users, Categories, Products, Addresses, Orders, and SSE endpoints.\n\nVariables auto-populate as you use the endpoints — start with Auth > Verify OTP to set your token.",
